{"id":1,"content":"<h2 style='text-align: center;'><span style='font-family:方正小标宋_GBK'>落实中央一号文件</span> <span style='font-family:方正小标宋_GBK'>保障国家粮食安全</span></h2><p style='text-indent: 43px;'>&nbsp;</p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>1.</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>正确</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>判断</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>确保重要农产品特别是粮食供给，是实施乡村振兴战略的首要任务。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>2.</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>正确</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>判断</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>解决好十几亿人口的吃饭问题，始终是我们党治国理政的头等大事。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>3.</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>正确</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>判断</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>保障国家粮食安全是一个永恒课题，任何时候这根弦都不能松。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>4.</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>正确</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>判断</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>当前，全球新冠肺炎疫情仍在蔓延，世界经济复苏脆弱，气候变化挑战突出，我国经济社会发展各项任务极为繁重艰巨。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>5.</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>正确</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>判断</span><span style='font-size:20px'> 2022</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>年中央一号文件提出全面落实粮食安全党政同责。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>6. <span style='color:red'>A</span> </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>单选</span><span style='font-size:20px'> 2013</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>年</span><span style='font-size:20px'>12</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>月</span><span style='font-size:20px'>23</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>日至</span><span style='font-size:20px'>24</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>日，中央农村工作会议在北京举行。习近平总书记在会上发表重要讲话指出，“洪范八政，（<span style='color:red'>食</span>）为政首。”</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>A </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>食</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>B </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>货</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>C </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>祀</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>D </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>司空</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>7. <span style='color:red'>D</span> </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>单选</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>在现阶段，我国社会主要矛盾已经转化为人民日益增长的（<span style='color:red'>美好生活</span>）需要和（<span style='color:red'>不平衡不充分</span>）的发展之间的矛盾。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>A </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>美好生活；不充实不均等</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>B </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>幸福生活；不平衡不充分</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>C </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>幸福生活；不充实不均等</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>D </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>美好生活；不平衡不充分</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>8. <span style='color:red'>B</span> </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>单选</span><span style='font-size:20px'> 2022</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>年中央一号文件提出坚持中国人的饭碗任何时候都要牢牢端在自己手中，饭碗主要装（<span style='color:red'>中国粮</span>）。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>A </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>人民粮</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>B </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>中国粮</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>C </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>安全粮</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>D </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>主产粮</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>9. <span style='color:red'>BC</span> </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>多选</span><span style='font-size:20px'> 2022</span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>年中央一号文件提出要牢牢守住（）两条底线。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>A </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>农业稳产增产</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>B </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>保障国家粮食安全</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>C </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>不发生规模性返贫</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>D </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312'>农民稳步增收</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px'>10.<span style='color:red'> ABCD</span> </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>多选</span> <span style='font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312'>关于确保我国粮食安全，我国要坚持以我为主，（）的国家粮食安全战略。</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>A </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>立足国内</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>B </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>确保产能</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>C </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>适度进口</span></p><p style='text-indent:48px'><span style='font-size:20px;color:red'>D </span><span style='font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:red'>科技支撑</span></p><p><br></p>"}